    "body": "Thanks for the example, but the workaround that you are already using is the way to go. Those functions are built to provide information to InstantSearch about the widgets state. Then the routing module use those functions to compute the URL. You are completely on track! \r\n\r\nHere is [an example](https://codesandbox.io/s/yz2nnnl61) that implements those methods with a custom places widget.",
